.product.product-single
  .range
    .cell-sm-8.cell-md-6
      .product-image
        img.img-responsive(src=product.images[0].src alt=product.images[0].alt).product-image-area
        - if (product.images.length)
        ul.product-thumbnails
          each image, index in product.images
            li(data-large-image=image.src class= (index == 0) ? "active" : "")
              img.img-responsive(src=image.thumb alt=image.alt width=image.width height=image.height)

    .cell-sm-12.cell-md-6.text-left.offset-top-41.offset-md-top-0
      // Product Brand
      p.product-brand.text-italic.text-dark= product.brand
      // Product Title
      h1.product-title.offset-top-0
        a(href= cfg.nav.shop.submenu.singleProduct.submenu.noSidebar.href)= product.title

      // Product Rating
      .product-rating.offset-top-20
        span.mdi.mdi-star
        span.mdi.mdi-star
        span.mdi.mdi-star
        span.mdi.mdi-star-half
        span.mdi.mdi-star-outline
        span.product-review-count.text-dark= product.reviews + " customer reviews"

      +accordion-classic(['Description', 'Size & Fit', 'Delivery & Returns'])
        div
          | Fashion has always been so temporary and uncertain. You can’t keep up with it. This social phenomenon is very whimsical, thus we as the consumers always try to stay in touch with all the latest fashion tendencies.
        div
          | 17.25" bust #[br] 14" shoulder to shoulder #[br] 32.25" shoulder to hem #[br]  Measurements taken from size small #[br] Model wears size small. Model is 5'9 #[br]  This dress fits true to size
        div
          | We deliver our goods worldwide. No matter where you live, your order will be shipped in time and delivered right to your door or to any other location you have stated. The packages are handled with utmost care, so the ordered products will be handed to you safe and sound, just like you expect them to be.

      .product-radio-wrap.product-radio-color.offset-top-34
        h5.product-radio-title(style="min-width: 130px;") Colors
        .form-group.offset-top-10.offset-xs-top-0
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-color", value="color-1", type="radio")
            span.product-radio(style="background-color: #1d2f61")
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-color", value="color-2", type="radio")
            span.product-radio(style="background-color: #9291a0")
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-color", value="color-3", type="radio")
            span.product-radio(style="background-color: #f3f1f2")

      .product-radio-wrap.offset-top-24
        h5.product-radio-title(style="min-width: 130px;") Select Size
        .form-group.offset-top-10.offset-xs-top-0
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-size", value="size-1", type="radio")
            span.small.product-radio XS
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-size", value="size-2", type="radio")
            span.small.product-radio S
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-size", value="size-3", type="radio")
            span.small.product-radio M
          label.radio-inline
            input(name="input-group-radio-size", value="size-4", type="radio")
            span.small.product-radio L

      // Product price
      .product-price.text-bold.h1.offset-top-34
        - if (typeof(product.price) == 'string'){
        span= '$' + product.price
        -}else{
        span.product-price-new= "$" + product.price[1]
        span.product-price-old.text-dark.small= '$' + product.price[0]
        -}

      .offset-top-34

        .form-group.product-number
          label.text-dark Quantity:
